	        Send us your pictures   ·  Send us your stories KOKSTAD SAPS are appealing to members of the community for assistance in locating a missing person. Michyle Samuel Fenner (20) of Hagan Place, Kokstad, was last seen on March 24 in Kokstad. He was wearing black Levi’s jeans, a black T-shirt and grey cap. He is 1,64 m tall and has black hair. “We appeal to anyone with information of his whereabouts to contact Warrant Officer Steven Strydom at 039 797 1123 or our Crime Stop number 086 00 10111,” said police spokesperson Captain Nqobile Gwala. — Supplied. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  